						<div class="postbody">I'm away from my computer, but I think I understand you...<br /><br />So my code does...<br />++Room;<br />Room &amp;= 3; to keep it 0-3<br /><br />Changing to...<br />Room &amp;= 4;<br /><br />Won't work. It will merely keep you in room #0.<br /><br />You need to...<br />If (Room &gt; 4) Room = 0;</div>

					
